==English==

===Verb===
{{head|en|verb|head=[[get up]] [[on]] [[the]] [[wrong]] [[side]] [[of]] [[the]] [[bed]]}}

# {{idiomatic}} To feel [[irritable]]; to be in a bad [[mood]]; to have a bad [[day]] from the start, for no particular reason.
#: ''I think my boss '''got up on the wrong side of the bed''' this morning.  He's been grumpy all day.''

====Synonyms====
* [[get out of bed on the wrong side]]
* [[wake up on the wrong side of bed]]
* [[wake up on the wrong side of the bed]]

